        "text": "到那天，耶路撒冷必听到这样的话： “锡安啊，不要害怕！不要双手发软！"
      },
      "cnv": {
        "version_id": "CNV",
        "version_name": "新譯本",
        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "到了那日， 必有人對耶路撒冷說： “錫安哪！不要懼怕； 你的手不要下垂。"
      },
      "cunp": {
        "version_id": "CUNP",
        "version_name": "和合本新標點（神版）",
        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "當那日，必有話向耶路撒冷說： 不要懼怕！錫安哪； 不要手軟！"
      },
      "nasb": {
        "version_id": "NASB",
        "version_name": "New American Standard Bible",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "In that day it will be said to Jerusalem: “Do not be afraid, O Zion; Do not let your hands fall limp."
      },
      "niv": {
        "version_id": "NIV",
        "version_name": "New International Version",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "On that day they will say to Jerusalem, “Do not fear, Zion; do not let your hands hang limp."
      },
      "nlt": {
        "version_id": "NLT",
        "version_name": "New Living Translation",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "On that day the announcement to Jerusalem will be, “Cheer up, Zion! Don’t be afraid!"
      }
